revision                0

description             Minimal coding agent written in Rust
long_description        zerostack is a minimalistic coding agent written in Rust, optimized for memory footprint and performance. \
                        It supports multiple LLM providers, a terminal UI, sessions, MCP servers, web search, looped coding tasks, \
                        and git worktree workflows.

